              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>A large and out-of-control Fontaine Research Institute of Kinetic Energy Engineering device. During combat, it will channel ousia energy to unleash a Gravity Reduction Field. Characters within this field can jump significantly higher. When the device is in this state, its Gravity Reduction Field will shut down if its core is annihilated by <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Pneuma attacks.</span></p>"
                ]
              }
